      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, but it's a bit broad. I want to really lean into the \"radicalism\" aspect to make the contrast sharper. Can you add a section that specifically calls out how these progressive policies are actually hurting families? Use some more aggressive language to frame it as a direct threat to the American way of life.",
